body:
Facing the same issue as well.
Stepping into the code, the error is raised because the operations dictionary doesn't have `QuantizedAdd` but has `QuantizedBiasAdd` instead, [line 279 of _importer.py_](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/python/framework/importer.py#L279)

[Contents of the operation dictionary](http://imgur.com/a/kvHIi)
_It has 629 elements so this image previews the Q elements segment only_
